Sqoop 安装
Please download it from here :
http://archive.cloudera.com/cdh5/cdh/5/sqoop-1.4.6-cdh5.5.2.tar.gz 

Unzip it to your local folder
Update /etc/profile to set the environment variables:
sudo vi /etc/profile
SQOOP_HOME=/Users/evenchen/Documents/Hadoop/sqoop
PATH=$SQOOP_HOME/bin:$PATH
export SQOOP_HOME
export PATH

And go to $SQOOP_HOME/conf, edit sqoop-env.sh,
Update HADOOP_COMMON_HOME and HADOOP_MAPRED_HOME to your $HADOOP_HOME;and also update HIVE_HOME to your $HIVE_HOME;

Go to command line, and type ‘sqoop help’, if no issue, then means installation successful.
